'''印度－塞舌爾關係'''，是指[[印度共和國|印度共和國]]和[[塞舌爾共和國|塞舌爾共和國]]之間的雙邊關係。印度在塞舌爾首都[[維多利亞_(塞舌爾)|維多利亞]]設有[[高級專員|高級專員]]公署，塞舌爾亦在印度首都[[新德里|新德里]]也設高級專員公署<ref>{{cite web|title=High Commission of India, Seychelles|url=http://www.seychelles.net/hicomind/|accessdate=28 December 2012|archive-date=2013-07-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130707090335/http://www.seychelles.net/hicomind/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 概況 ==
自塞舌爾在1976年獨立以來，印度與塞舌爾已經存在外交關係。1987年，印度在塞舌爾首都維多利亞開設了高級專員公署，塞舌爾亦在2008年於新德里設立駐印度外交機構。印度和塞舌爾兩國的關係一直緊密友好，亦有定期的高層互訪。[[印度總理|印度總理]][[英迪拉·甘地|英迪拉·甘地]]、[[印度總統|印度總統]][[拉馬斯瓦米·文卡塔拉曼|拉馬斯瓦米·文卡塔拉曼]]及[[普拉蒂巴·帕蒂爾|普拉蒂巴·帕蒂爾]]曾到塞舌爾外訪<ref>{{cite news|title=President arrives in Seychelles on a 2-day visit|url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/industry-and-economy/economy/article3367300.ece|accessdate=28 December 2012|newspaper=Hindu Businessline|archive-date=2012-07-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120701204330/http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/industry-and-economy/economy/article3367300.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而[[塞舌爾總統|塞舌爾總統]][[弗朗斯-阿爾貝·勒內|弗朗斯-阿爾貝·勒內]]和[[詹姆斯·米歇爾|詹姆斯·米歇爾]]上校亦曾國事訪問印度<ref>{{cite web|title=Indo-Seychelles Bilateral Relations|url=http://www.seychelles.net/hicomind/indosey.html|accessdate=28 December 2012|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121018113801/http://seychelles.net/hicomind/indosey.html|archivedate=2012年10月18日}}</ref>。兩國在[[軍事|軍事]]、[[文化|文化]]、[[經貿|經貿]]和[[科技|科技]]等領域均有合作。[[印度外交部|印度外交部]]曾形容兩國之間的關係是“親密的友誼、理解和合作”<ref>http://mea.gov.in/mystart.php?id=50044520</ref>，塞舌爾亦曾形容自己是“印度在[[印度洋|印度洋]]地區可靠的夥伴”<ref>{{cite news|title=Seychelles says it would be 'rock of dependability' for India|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/seychelles-says-it-would-be-rock-of-dependability-for-india/article3370486.ece|accessdate=28 December 2012|newspaper=The Hindu|date=April 30, 2012}}</ref>。

== 經貿關係 ==
於2010-11年，印度和塞舌爾兩國之間的雙邊貿易總額為4000萬美元<ref>{{cite news|title=President to lead business delegations to Seychelles, S. Africa|url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/industry-and-economy/government-and-policy/president-to-lead-business-delegations-to-seychelles-s-africa/article3361312.ece|accessdate=28 December 2012|newspaper=The Hindu Businessline|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20130204065816/http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/industry-and-economy/government-and-policy/president-to-lead-business-delegations-to-seychelles-s-africa/article3361312.ece|archivedate=2013年2月4日}}</ref>。兩國在[[旅遊業|旅遊業]]、[[漁業|漁業]]、[[石油勘探|石油勘探]]、[[資訊及通訊科技|資訊及通訊科技]]、[[藥物|藥物]]等經濟領域均有合作<ref>{{cite news|title=Economic diplomacy important: Pratibha|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/article3396733.ece?css=print|accessdate=28 December 2012|newspaper=The Hindu|date=May 8, 2012}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Seychelles keen on trade pact with India|url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.in/2005/08/02/stories/2005080203200700.htm|accessdate=28 December 2012|newspaper=The Hindu Businessline|date=August 2, 2005|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714234517/http://www.thehindubusinessline.in/2005/08/02/stories/2005080203200700.htm|archivedate=2014年7月14日|df=}}</ref>。印度和塞舌爾兩國於2010及2012年簽署了雙邊投資促進協定，印度提高借貸予塞舌爾的[[信用額度|信用額度]]至5000萬[[美元|美元]]，又提供2500萬元的援助<ref name="thehindu">{{cite news|title=India reaches out to Seychelles|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/article3371397.ece|accessdate=28 December 2012|newspaper=The Hindu|date=April 30, 2012|archive-date=2012-07-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120704092149/http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/article3371397.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Seychelles, Mauritius keen on attracting Indian investments|url=http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/industry-and-economy/article3935383.ece|accessdate=28 December 2012|newspaper=The Hindu Businessline|archive-date=2012-10-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121027132058/http://www.thehindubusinessline.com/industry-and-economy/article3935383.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。印度私營企業中，大型電訊商{{Link-en|Airtel|Bharti Airtel}}在塞舌爾有着重要的地位，它既收購塞舌爾電訊，又參與東非海底光纜項目<ref>{{cite news|title=Bharti to invest $10 mn in Seychelles|url=http://www.livemint.com/Companies/tdG3iD9DeGZOtpD9Byg4IP/Bharti-to-invest-10-mn-in-Seychelles.html|accessdate=28 December 2012|newspaper=HT Mint|date=August 17, 2010|archive-date=2019-05-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190516181235/https://www.livemint.com/Companies/tdG3iD9DeGZOtpD9Byg4IP/Bharti-to-invest-10-mn-in-Seychelles.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 軍事關係 ==
印度和塞舌爾兩國有著密切的防務關係。由於塞舌爾靠近全球航運和貿易的通道，該國對印度在打擊海上[[恐怖主義|恐怖主義]]和[[海盜|海盜]]方面有重要的戰略意義<ref>{{cite news|title=India will work with Seychelles against piracy, terror: President|url=http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/india-will-work-with-seychelles-against-piracy-terror-president/article3366778.ece|accessdate=28 December 2012|newspaper=The Hindu|date=April 29, 2012|archive-date=2020-06-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200627124131/https://www.thehindu.com/news/national/India-will-work-with-Seychelles-against-piracy-terror-President/article12981924.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。1987年6月，[[印度海軍|印度海軍]]在塞舌爾[[維多利亞港_(塞席爾)|維多利亞港]]部署了一艘{{link-en|INS ''Vindhyagiri'' (F42)|INS Vindhyagiri (F42)}}戰艦<ref>{{cite web|title=India’s Sea Power Status Going Into the Future An Appreciation|url=http://www.dsalert.org/naval-power-india/521-indias-sea-power-status-going-into-the-future-an-appreciation|publisher=Defence and Security Alert|accessdate=13 March 2013|archive-date=2019-05-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190514090110/http://www.dsalert.org/naval-power-india/521-indias-sea-power-status-going-into-the-future-an-appreciation|dead-url=yes}}</ref>；2009年，印度接受塞舌爾的請求，派遣海軍艦艇，協助塞舌爾打擊海盜<ref>{{cite news|title=Navy responds to SOS from Seychelles|url=http://www.indianexpress.com/news/navy-responds-to-sos-from-seychelles/449049/0|accessdate=28 December 2012|newspaper=The Indian Express|date=April 20, 2009|archive-date=2009-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090515221443/http://www.indianexpress.com/news/navy-responds-to-sos-from-seychelles/449049/0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。印度又向塞舌爾提供資金，協助該國建設[[軍隊|軍隊]]<ref>{{cite news|title=India to assist Seychelles in anti-piracy operations|url=http://www.hindu.com/2010/07/20/stories/2010072061850900.htm|accessdate=28 December 2012|newspaper=The Hindu|date=July 20, 2010|archive-date=2013-01-26|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130126005638/http://www.hindu.com/2010/07/20/stories/2010072061850900.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=India to discuss security ties with Seychelles|url=http://www.hindu.com/2010/06/02/stories/2010060262591400.htm|accessdate=28 December 2012|newspaper=The Hindu|date=June 2, 2010|archive-date=2013-01-25|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130125100636/http://www.hindu.com/2010/06/02/stories/2010060262591400.htm|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=Bharti Airtel to acquire Telecom Seychelles|url=http://www.thehindu.com/business/companies/article564347.ece|accessdate=28 December 2012|newspaper=The Hindu|date=August 11, 2010|archive-date=2012-07-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120717113848/http://www.thehindu.com/business/companies/article564347.ece|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

